nd search Phenic, <br>-give him the water and you will get exp and his water. <br>-Now, give Phenics water back to Arbogast<br>-you get Silver Wrappings<br><br>you say, who is tsap katta? <br>you say, who is nathyn? <br><br>-now go back the iceway, you will see two sonic wolves, step in the house<br>You will need a rogue here who can picklock the door, <br>once the door is open step in and A Coterie Servant will spawn, he has an AE stun with knowback, back form the door, if youre a caster forget it, you spells will be interupptet every time, my epic rune hold long enogh that he was oom, but he hits fast for about 80, your rogue can kill him easy<br><br>-pick up the book you see on the table and combine the book in your Silver Wrappings<br><br>-Now give this item back to Arbogast<br>he give you Gold Wrappings<br><br>you say, norrath does exist <br>you say, what exodus<br><br>-now go to Shadow Haven and find Peqi<br><br>To find him, walk across the <br>bridge heading away from the library/caster/monk guild. Right as you step off the bridge, <br>turn right, walk foward, and open the second door on your right - Peqi spawns infront of <br>the flower pot. heard its a 24h spawn, but i think about 6h or so..<br>so now, just kill him very easy and no faction<br>lewt up the book and combine it in your Gold Wrappings<br><br>-Now back in katta give Arbogast your combined item <br><br>-He gives you Black Wrappings<br><br>you say, what expedition? <br><br>-now head to akheva in maidens <br>if youre lvl 60 you can kill there solo (as an wizard)if not get a little guildgroup. <br>noone there see invis so go a bit in and try to find &quot;The Protector&quot; kill him and lewt if he has &quot;Akuel Xi Ans Vius&quot; <br>you need 2 of them to combine them and crap there no rent, so pewl more its easy to get 2, if you go ld or so make a duel corpse and leave the akuel xi ans vius on it.<br>-now, combine the both Akuel Xi Ans Vius in your Black Wrappings<br><br>-now, get a 60tank and a 60healer (if youre in a smaller guild get a full group of War Enc Rog and Clr all 50 to 55,)<br><br>you get your Tank and Healer? Alright, <br>-Give Arbogst The combinet Item and he will say, that you have to follow him to the bank ( miller follows too ) <br>in the bank they say, that they keep it and run back in the bar, both need to be aggro on you so attack both, <br>noone guard or npc will assist so easy kill, <br><br>-now lewt up from Arbogast the shield, and from Miller a Combine Container, with cloak look,<br>combine the shield in the cloak and you get your <br>Cloak of the truth <br><br>Good luck all who want to have this, its not nd so very nice twink item <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>  <br>-Diceeno Dunkelrose- <br>Epic Sorcerer SolusekRo  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uetheon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Etheon</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(12/27/01 5:21:11 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm35.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Cloak of Truth - Spoiler</span><hr size=1> So couldnt you just skip all that stuff, and just kill that guy you kill last? Loot his stuff and combine it. <p><body vlink="#0000FF" alink="#0000FF"><div align="center"><img src=http://members.aol.com/erichq2/etheon.jpg width="474" height="75"><br>Etheon, 55<sup>th</sup> lvl Evoker<br>Profile | <a href=http://www.veilofsilence.org>Veil of Silence</a> | <a href=http://www.innoruuk.com>Innoruuk</a> | <a href=mailto:EricHQ2@aol.com>E-Mail</a></div></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20%